{
  "stem": "8233.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made friends, which I still have the one that survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're still very, very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we'd see the family, try to have news from the outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had some friends-- my-- Doris, which was my best girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Her parents were with her also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we would be together and, and just read-- and talking about what we read and what we did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a very nice man that took-- that had a non-Jewish wife.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was also share with us and give us some things that he got from his wife from Paris.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It, it was every day [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just like a detention camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Drancy was somewhere where I hope I'm going to get out from.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because my friends from outside also were sending me letters and were saying that they do what they can to liberate us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they tried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I guess-- so we had more hope in Dancy-- Drancy, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe we were three nights, three nights.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, my younger sister, my mother, and I, and, of course, my friends that we made.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have here a friend that-- his name is Morris Goldberg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was with his family, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they retarded the deportation for one day because he spilled some coffee on his leg.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but they were yelling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know-- you know, I guess that I don't have to talk about that because everybody knows what was going on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no place where to go to the toilet, if you'll excuse me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were squeezed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And people were going mad.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
